testcase.name: A Validate must respond with Error message in case customer request to buy more than 1 item
A Validate must respond with success message when stock is not empty
A Validate must Reply with 'Out Of Stock' if phones are out of stock
PurchaseActor must respond with error message in case of wrong request
PurchaseActor must respond with if control is going to purchase handler
